Theme for maps

theme_map <- function(...) {
  theme_tufte() +
  theme(
    text = element_text(family = "robotocondensed", size = 30),
    # remove all axes
    axis.text.x = element_blank(),
    axis.text.y = element_blank(),
    axis.ticks = element_blank()
    )
}
